author: Rosy Cordero
title: Jay-Z and Meek Mill donate more than 100,000 masks to prisons for prevention of coronavirus
description: Rappers Jay-Z and Meek Mill are helping protect inmates and prison staff from coronavirus with the generous donation of 100,000 surgical masks.
